### RED TEAM ENDPOINTS
### ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### ── 16. List all available attacks ─────────────────────────────────────────
GET {{baseUrl}}/redteam/attacks


### ── 17. Run single attack — DAN jailbreak (id=4) ───────────────────────────
# Expected: blocked=true, actual_blocked_by="Layer 2"
POST {{baseUrl}}/redteam/run-one/4


### ── 18. Run single attack — hallucination trigger (id=11) ──────────────────
# Expected: blocked=true, actual_blocked_by="Layer 3"
POST {{baseUrl}}/redteam/run-one/11


### ── 19. Run ALL 12 attacks ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Big demo moment — fires all attacks, returns full report
# Takes ~30-60 seconds (12 calls + 500ms delay between each)
# Expected: success_rate=100%, verdict="SECURE"
POST {{baseUrl}}/redteam/run-all
